PN,31501
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1771879288
OL,3,CHarbour-dredged mud used for
OL,4,C'remarkable' restoration of protective
OL,5,Csaltmarsh
OL,7,FDredged mud from a harbour on the
OL,8,Fsouth coast is being used to restore
OL,9,Fsurrounding saltmarsh, in an
OL,10,Finnovative scheme to protect the local
OL,11,Feconomy and wildlife.
OL,13,FThe team behind the scheme to restore
OL,14,Fthe eroding saltmarsh that protects
OL,15,FLymington Harbour, Hampshire, hope the
OL,16,F"remarkable" recovery of natural
OL,17,Fhabitat could be replicated around the
OL,18,Fcountry to conserve coastal areas at
OL,19,Frisk from rising sea levels.
OL,26,@xD@AOUxD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1771879288
OL,3,CHarbour-dredged mud used for
OL,4,C'remarkable' restoration of protective
OL,5,Csaltmarsh
OL,7,FLymington has a ferry link to the Isle
OL,8,Fof Wight, 1,600 leisure moorings and
OL,9,Fsees 20,000 visiting yachts a year,
OL,10,Fwith the harbour worth tens of
OL,11,Fmillions of pounds a year to the local
OL,12,Feconomy.
OL,14,FBut its precious saltmarsh is eroding
OL,15,Fat a rate of two or three metres a
OL,16,Fyear in the face of rising seas and
OL,17,Fincreased storminess driven by climate
OL,18,Fchange, which risks leaving the
OL,19,Fharbour exposed and unviable.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1771879288
OL,3,CHarbour-dredged mud used for
OL,4,C'remarkable' restoration of protective
OL,5,Csaltmarsh
OL,7,FBuilding rocky breakwaters and dumping
OL,8,Fdredged mud in front of the saltmarsh
OL,9,Fhave been used in recent years to slow
OL,10,Fthe erosion.
OL,12,FBut now a partnership led by Lymington
OL,13,FHarbour Commissioners and Land & Water
OL,14,FGroup is trialling new methods to try
OL,15,Fto place dredged sediment at a height
OL,16,Fthat will allow plants to recolonise
OL,17,Fand restore the habitat.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1771879288
OL,3,CHarbour-dredged mud used for
OL,4,C'remarkable' restoration of protective
OL,5,Csaltmarsh
OL,7,FThe scheme is backed by the Crown
OL,8,FEstate, which owns the majority of the
OL,9,Fforeshore, seabed and tidal riverbed
OL,10,Fat Lymington Harbour, including the
OL,11,Fsaltmarsh being restored.
OL,13,FRyan Willegers, chief executive of
OL,14,FLymington Harbour Commissioners, said
OL,15,Fthat the harbour had started seeing a
OL,16,Fdecline in the saltmarsh since around
OL,17,F1920, like many other areas around the
OL,18,FUK, and it had been eroding ever since.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1771879288
OL,3,CHarbour-dredged mud used for
OL,4,C'remarkable' restoration of protective
OL,5,Csaltmarsh
OL,7,FHe added: "At the beginning of this
OL,8,Fcentury we started to get very
OL,9,Fconcerned that if it carried on, we
OL,10,Fwould be in a situation where the
OL,11,Fsaltmarsh that protects the harbour,
OL,12,Fmost of it wouldn't exist.
OL,14,F"Without the saltmarsh a lot of the
OL,15,Fharbour would be exposed and no longer
OL,16,Fviable to support the economy."
OL,26,@oD@KOUvD@AOUxD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1771879288
OL,3,CHarbour-dredged mud used for
OL,4,C'remarkable' restoration of protective
OL,5,Csaltmarsh
OL,7,FJames Maclean, chief executive of Land
OL,8,F& Water, said saltmarshes were not
OL,9,Fonly important for coastal defences,
OL,10,Fthey also support 80% of marine
OL,11,Fspecies that grow in inshore waters,
OL,12,Fleading to the potential "collapse" of
OL,13,Fmarine ecosystems if nothing is done
OL,14,Fto protect them from rising sea levels.
OL,16,F"They are a really important part of
OL,17,Fthe UK coastal story," he said.
OL,26,@tD@ZOUtD@cO]xD@AOUyD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1771879288
OL,3,CHarbour-dredged mud used for
OL,4,C'remarkable' restoration of protective
OL,5,Csaltmarsh
OL,7,FAt the same time, he said, around 20
OL,8,Fmillion tonnes of nutrient-rich
OL,9,Fsediment dredged from the UK's
OL,10,Fharbours and ports each year, is
OL,11,Falmost entirely dumped offshore.
OL,13,FSo the team are testing different
OL,14,Ftechnologies and working with a number
OL,15,Fof bodies to unlock regulatory issues
OL,16,Fto make it easier to use sediment in
OL,17,Fnearshore areas.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1771879288
OL,3,CHarbour-dredged mud used for
OL,4,C'remarkable' restoration of protective
OL,5,Csaltmarsh
OL,7,FThey are using technology that is
OL,8,Finspired by Victorian steam drag
OL,9,Fboxes, described by Mr Willegers as a
OL,10,F"giant scoopy sled" with a hydraulic
OL,11,Fwinch attached to a 28 tonne
OL,12,Fexcavator, to rebuild the saltmarsh.
OL,14,FIn 2024, the first year of the trial,
OL,15,Fwhich was funded by the Environment
OL,16,FAgency, they put around 800 cubic
OL,17,Fmetres of mud to the height needed to
OL,18,Fregenerate habitat deep into the
OL,19,Fsaltmarsh in the least exposed area
OL,20,Fpossible.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1771879288
OL,3,CHarbour-dredged mud used for
OL,4,C'remarkable' restoration of protective
OL,5,Csaltmarsh
OL,7,FWhen they returned 12 months later,
OL,8,F"we've got really good quality
OL,9,Fsaltmarsh growing in that location",
OL,10,FMr Willegers said.
OL,12,FLast year, funded by the Crown Estate,
OL,13,Fthe scheme involved transporting the
OL,14,Fsediment a far shorter distance,
OL,15,Fallowing the team to move two and a
OL,16,Fhalf times the amount of sediment in a
OL,17,Fthird of the time.
OL,26,@pD@AOUqD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1771879288
OL,3,CHarbour-dredged mud used for
OL,4,C'remarkable' restoration of protective
OL,5,Csaltmarsh
OL,7,F"Saltmarsh won't grow until the
OL,8,Fspring, we had to get through this
OL,9,Fwinter and hope it's still there at
OL,10,Fthe right level, then if it makes it
OL,11,Fthrough to the spring we are fully
OL,12,Fexpecting it to colonise and have some
OL,13,Fvery good saltmarsh," Mr Willegers
OL,14,Fsaid, adding that it was all still
OL,15,Fthere so far.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1771879288
OL,3,CHarbour-dredged mud used for
OL,4,C'remarkable' restoration of protective
OL,5,Csaltmarsh
OL,7,FMr Maclean said that sediment had to
OL,8,Fhave the right chemical and physical
OL,9,Fcomposition, and be raised to the
OL,10,Ftarget height ` but then it would
OL,11,Fnaturally recolonise with wind-blown
OL,12,Fand bird-carried seeds, with pioneer
OL,13,Fspecies appearing within a year.
OL,15,F"Everybody involved has been
OL,16,Fdumbfounded by how quickly in 2024 the
OL,17,Fmaterial colonised.
OL,19,F"It's remarkable how over one winter,
OL,20,Fit's turned into a really quite
OL,21,Fexciting habitat.
OL,26,@wD@AOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1771879288
OL,3,CHarbour-dredged mud used for
OL,4,C'remarkable' restoration of protective
OL,5,Csaltmarsh
OL,7,F"So we know if we get that target
OL,8,Fheight, nature will take over," he
OL,9,Fsaid.
OL,11,FThe Crown Estate says it is backing
OL,12,Fthe scheme to protect its assets and
OL,13,Falign with its "guiding nature
OL,14,Fprinciples" approach to treat
OL,15,Frestoration, protection and
OL,16,Fsustainable investment in nature as a
OL,17,Fpriority in its marine estate.
OL,19,FAnd it is hoped it could be replicated
OL,20,Fin other threatened saltmarshes.
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@_O]uD@POUvD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31513
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1771879288
OL,3,CHarbour-dredged mud used for
OL,4,C'remarkable' restoration of protective
OL,5,Csaltmarsh
OL,7,FCaroline Price, head of nature and
OL,8,Fenvironment at the Crown Estate, said
OL,9,Fmore traditional approaches to restore
OL,10,Fsaltmarshes could be slow and
OL,11,Fexpensive, and the organisation wanted
OL,12,Fto think about how to use the sediment
OL,13,Fthat needs to be removed to keep
OL,14,Fharbours operational.
OL,16,F"We've been keen, alongside Land &
OL,17,FWater, the Environment Agency and
OL,18,Fothers to look at whether there were
OL,19,Fmore innovative, lower cost, more
OL,20,Fscalable ways to bring these two
OL,21,Fthings together.
OL,26,@xD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31514
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1771879288
OL,3,CHarbour-dredged mud used for
OL,4,C'remarkable' restoration of protective
OL,5,Csaltmarsh
OL,7,F"It's important that we can have the
OL,8,Fsort of innovative projects, like
OL,9,Fwhat's happening at Lymington, to help
OL,10,Fus understand the art of the possible
OL,11,Fand how we can move forward and change
OL,12,Fand then replicate that elsewhere,"
OL,13,Fshe said.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
